{"type": "article", "id": 29175, "title": "陈列柜", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-05T22:53:30Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 31, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160705230100Oiuf3FT1y6EASQPe.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>巴黎的工作室 <a href=\"http://www.aplusacooren.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">A+A Cooren</a> 由一对来自法国和日本的设计师夫妇组成，他们最近接受了艺术家兼收藏家客户们的委托，为一间改造的小木屋设计了一款名为“好奇心陈列柜”（Cabinet of curiosities）的家具，用来展示他们五花八门的收藏品。陈列柜由纤细的蓝色金属支架、内部漆上蓝色的木质收纳盒以及白色的搁板构成。这些组件摆放的位置并不对称，加上打开的半开放式抽屉，有一种随性却又统一的简约美感。可惜的是，这个漂亮的陈列柜目前还未投入量产。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160705230118fqRyOWLCSJT9IsD2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.624694\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160705230118AmINaFbRVMDeZlBf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.744499\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160705230118s8CR6VTQUFj2ZvYw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.811736\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160705230120B0R2aeEmoIixksQU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.953545\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}